<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und kauffleute
                            <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchleuht<ex>ikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> reden werden von
                            <expan>solch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freyheiten und gnaden, die wir von
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vordern, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>selig<ex>en</ex></expan> gedehtnüsse
                        in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lande<ex>n</ex></expan> und herschäfften
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc.
                        ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan>
<expan>trinitat<ex>em</ex></expan> anno <expan>deci<ex>m</ex>o</expan>.</ab>
